text: Buaran station is a commuter rail station that is part of the KAI Commuter Jabodetabek system, and is located in Jl. I Gusti Ngurah Rai, Penggillingan, Cakung, East Jakarta, and is part of the rail system's "Zone 1". The elevation of this station is +11 m. ==Trains and services== The lines below are the lines that stop and serve in the Buaran station. *Blue Line: to Jakarta Kota and Bekasi Category:East Jakarta Category:Railway stations in Jakarta
